| Query/select | `get [nodeId]` | READ-ONLY | Gets properties of node/selection. |
| Query/select | `inspect <nodeId> [--json] [--spec]` | READ-ONLY | Emits positioning/spec properties. |
| Query/select | `select <nodeId>` | MUTATING | Changes current selection only. |
| Duplicate/delete | `duplicate|dup [nodeId] [--offset n]` | MUTATING | Duplicates node/selection. |
| Duplicate/delete | `delete|remove [nodeId]` | DESTRUCTIVE | Deletes node/selection. |
