| Node | `node to-component <nodeIds...>` | MUTATING | Converts frames to components. |
| Node | `node delete <nodeIds...>` | DESTRUCTIVE | Deletes nodes by ID. |
| Slots | `slot list [nodeId]` | READ-ONLY | Lists slots. |
